data.name: Sample - OpenAI - 1.1.0
data.description: Sample playbooks for "OpenAI" connector. If you are planning to use any of the sample playbooks in your environment, ensure that you clone those playbooks and move them to a different collection, since the sample playbook collection gets deleted during connector upgrade and delete.

workflows.name: Ask a Question
workflows.description: Generates a completion for a given chat message using a pre-trained deep learning model.

arguments.name: OpenAI

workflows.name: Converse with OpenAI
workflows.description: Request a response based on previous questions/answers from OpenAI

arguments.name: OpenAI

workflows.name: Get Usage Report
workflows.description: Fetches the token usage per specified day

workflows.name: List Available Models
workflows.description: Fetches the list of currently available AI models from OpenAI
